      <biogHist id="md5-361cc8a0f8d73724a0e12bed48ede6fe">
        <p>Founded in 1972 as the Clothing Studies Association of Canada, the Apparel Studies Association of Canada Inc. was incorporated in 1973 and received its national charter in 1974.  Its aim was to support research and facilitate professional communication among clothing researchers and users of research through newsletters and general meetings.  Its head office was located in the Department of Clothing and Textiles at the University of Alberta.  The Association was dissolved in 1988.</p>
      </biogHist>
